title: Jesse Jane: Dirty Movies
overview: When Jesse has plans to leave the house for a few days, Manuel invites the boys over to view a few secret videotapes. Mick offers a tape that he secretly videotaped of Cindy and himself in a heated and sensual romp. Tommy then arrives to show the guys his tape, and it's very apparent that he's proud of his work! Jesse leaves Manuel a "love letter" that turns out to be his biggest nightmare...and every viewers fantasy.
